@startuml

title System Sequence Diagram for Saving Sentence to History
actor User
participant System

User -> System: requests to see sentence history

activate System

alt history found
    note right of System
        1. Retrieve public sentence history from the storage.
        2. Format the history for display.
    end note
    System --> User: displays sentence history
else no history found
    System --> User: displays message "No sentence history available"
else unexpected error
    System --> User: displays generic error message
end

deactivate System

@enduml